item.title: Other Apps
item.description: Travel guides and maps https://mytripnavi.com/maps/all/ Tired of filling out online checkin information over and over again, try out our new id fill-out assist app. https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mytripnavi.app.mypassdaruma mypass1 mypass2 mypass3 mypass4 mypass5 mypass6 mypass7 mypass8 https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mytripnavi.app.mypassdaruma Classic note pad for taking note and memo. No account needed, no distraction by a lot of functions and internet notification or sharing. This will help you to focus mainly on writing out what you want to write.
